'''斯宾塞·韦尔斯'''（{{lang-en|Rush Spencer Wells IV}}，{{bd|1969年|4月6日|}}）是一位[[美国|美国]][[遗传学|遗传学]]家和科普作家<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://randy-rootstech.blogspot.com/2014/02/dr-spencer-wells-talks-dna-and-genetics.html|title=Randy at RootsTech: Dr. Spencer Wells Talks DNA and Genetics - Friday Keynote #2|last=Seaver|first=Randy|date=2014-02-07|website=Randy at RootsTech|access-date=2018-07-18|archive-date=2019-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190124192431/http://randy-rootstech.blogspot.com/2014/02/dr-spencer-wells-talks-dna-and-genetics.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，主要科普作品有《{{le|人类的旅程：基因的奥德赛之旅|The Journey of Man: A Genetic Odyssey}}》（''The Journey of Man: A Genetic Odyssey''）等。
